# Data for WEAP modelling

## Hydrological boundaries
gandak_basin_ll.shp is the whole catchment
(India + Nepal), whereas gandak_basin_india_ll.shp
contains the portion of the basin downstream of the
barrage only.

## Land cover map
Globcover_2009_{cropland|forest|...|water_bodies}.tif
shows the land cover in the basin. Land cover itself
is not particularly dynamic (instead the growth of
irrigated area dominates, but we attempt to model
this process endogenously). I do have maps of
irrigated area for various crops, so let me know if
these would be helpful.

