## Meteorological inputs (meteo/*)
I've used a combination of IMD and PRINCETON
data for the meteorology (IMD + PRINCETON for
precipitation, PRINCETON for everything else). The
subdirectory doesn't contain all the variables you
requested because I precompute reference ET. I can
send these but the dataset is rather large (~14Gb),
so it may be just as easy for you to download the
data yourself.

